products.title: Fairhaven Carnival Roman Blind
products.description: This fairhaven carnival roman blind is such a wonderful choice, so contemporary and fresh. It's truly the best thing to lift a scheme into the now. The lovely watercolour floral pattern grows up the blind, fading out into the white of the fabric, keeping the vibrancy and punch.
